Last year, I approached the Lyric on behalf of my company to be a sponsor. I met with someone to talk about doing a "donation in kind" arrangement, at her suggsetion. I made it very clear that whether the Lyric wished to participate in this arrangement or not, my company would like to be a sponsor regardless. Unfortunately, I was not given the courtesy of a follow up even though I tried to follow up. Our company allocated funds another way. I'm disappointed that the Lyric doesn't regard a corporate sponsorship as being worthy enough to follow up with. My husband and I will still continue to support the Lyric.
